column2: "That is quite a large mob of Darkers. The largest I have seen."
"How so many have gathered in one place, I honestly have no idea."
"With such a vast numbers disadvantage, restoring order is going to prove difficult for the ARKS."
"Sometimes, it is hard to tell if we have the advantage, or if they do..."
"But as they say, you cannot win if you do not even try. I think that's the case here."
